{"tid":780070,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"晴報呢篇野算唔算侮辱咗成個Cosplay界？","createTime":"2018-08-15T01:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T05:30:16.000Z","uid":71740,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"09ff5451076380a022289736637c65b3425fa206","tid":780070,"uid":71740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T01:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/091059_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F091059_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=15268030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n－  晴報 2018.08.15<br />\n<br />\n我唔係Cosplayer，但見到呢篇評論都為佢地感到不忿。有行開C3/動漫節都知，人地做Cosplayer,背後係落咗幾多心機。呢條弱智入去行個轉，講幾句，就將人地既努力否定曬，仲踩埋佢所講既宅男，龍友，日本人幾班人。咁冇腦而大膽既寫法，希望佢只係想出位，或者俾班廢中老自high打飛機&hellip;如果唔係，我覺得佢個女都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw晴報究竟有冇審核過呢啲&ldquo;作者&rdquo;寫既野？呢啲文章俾d未有批判性思考既小朋友睇到，真係會歪曲咗佢地既價值觀。有冇咩途徑係有效既可以阻止晴報登呢啲劣質文章？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 非Colspayer，宅男，龍友，日本人"},{"pid":"f49fa2f26a728fdc260148d8be58c9eeaf0a55f5","tid":780070,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T01:46:05.000Z","msg":"有講錯咩=.="},{"pid":"f86da38c14e400b729be52feffe780135aa9f380","tid":780070,"uid":35667,"like":13,"dislike":6,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T01:46:49.000Z","msg":"好人好者邊會cosplay"},{"pid":"bb5bbb4099b5d87b500e0ecf5aace70886005e07","tid":780070,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T02:05:26.000Z","msg":"[晴報專訊]"},{"pid":"64d34e4886400c4281b7113ab05f2e41f84b7a88","tid":780070,"uid":3976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T02:10:23.000Z","msg":"我唔准佢咁話夏蕙姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b3bc6839f19ec750d22e6fdea5d4fe7b30cbc0","tid":780070,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":